PLACEHOLDER FOR NOTIFICATION SOUND

This file represents where the notification.mp3 audio file should be placed.

For production use, replace this placeholder with an actual MP3 audio file named "notification.mp3"

You can:
1. Record your own notification sound
2. Use a free sound from websites like:
   - freesound.org
   - zapsplat.com
   - soundbible.com

Recommended sound characteristics:
- Duration: 1-3 seconds
- Format: MP3
- Volume: Moderate to high
- Type: Pleasant notification chime or bell sound

The sound will play when a new order becomes ready to alert customers.
